<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Happy Birthday, Ja! 💖</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Quicksand:wght@400;600;700&family=Pacifico&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{
margin:0;
padding:0;
box-sizing:border-box;
}

body{
font-family:'Quicksand',sans-serif;
background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ffe6f2,#fff5fa,#ffeef5);
overflow:hidden;
height:100vh;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
position:relative;
}

/* Floating Hearts */
.hearts{
position:absolute;
width:100%;
height:100%;
overflow:hidden;
pointer-events:none;
}

.heart{
position:absolute;
font-size:25px;
animation:float 10s linear infinite;
opacity:.7;
}

@keyframes float{
0%{
transform:translateY(100vh) rotate(0deg);
opacity:0;
}
20%{
opacity:1;
}
100%{
transform:translateY(-120vh) rotate(360deg);
opacity:0;
}
}

.container{
text-align:center;
z-index:2;
}

h1{
font-family:'Pacifico',cursive;
color:#ff5d9e;
margin-bottom:15px;
font-size:3rem;
text-shadow:2px 2px white;
}

.subtitle{
color:#666;
margin-bottom:30px;
font-size:18px;
}

/* Envelope */

.envelope{
width:240px;
height:160px;
margin:auto;
position:relative;
cursor:pointer;
transition:.4s;
animation:bounce 2s infinite;
}

.envelope:hover{
transform:scale(1.08);
}

@keyframes bounce{
0%,100%{
transform:translateY(0);
}
50%{
transform:translateY(-12px);
}
}

.back{
position:absolute;
width:100%;
height:100%;
background:#ffb6d5;
border-radius:10px;
}

.flap{
position:absolute;
top:0;
left:0;
width:0;
height:0;
border-left:120px solid transparent;
border-right:120px solid transparent;
border-top:90px solid #ff8fbe;
transform-origin:top;
transition:1s;
z-index:4;
}

.letter{
position:absolute;
left:15px;
top:15px;
width:210px;
height:130px;
background:white;
border-radius:8px;
display:flex;
justify-content:center;
align-items:center;
font-size:20px;
color:#ff5d9e;
font-weight:bold;
transition:1s;
z-index:2;
}

.envelope.open .flap{
transform:rotateX(180deg);
}

.envelope.open .letter{
transform:translateY(-180px);
}

/* Popup */

.popup{
position:fixed;
top:50%;
left:50%;
transform:translate(-50%,-50%) scale(0);
width:90%;
max-width:700px;
height:80%;
background:white;
border-radius:25px;
padding:30px;
overflow-y:auto;
box-shadow:0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.25);
transition:.5s;
z-index:100;
}

.popup.show{
transform:translate(-50%,-50%) scale(1);
}

.popup h2{
font-family:'Pacifico';
color:#ff5d9e;
text-align:center;
margin-bottom:20px;
}

.popup p{
line-height:1.9;
font-size:17px;
color:#555;
white-space:pre-line;
}

.close{
position:absolute;
right:20px;
top:15px;
font-size:28px;
cursor:pointer;
color:#ff5d9e;
}

.footer{
text-align:center;
margin-top:30px;
font-size:20px;
color:#ff5d9e;
font-weight:bold;
}

.sparkle{
position:absolute;
font-size:25px;
animation:twinkle 2s infinite alternate;
}

@keyframes twinkle{
from{
opacity:.3;
transform:scale(.8);
}
to{
opacity:1;
transform:scale(1.2);
}
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- Background Music -->
<audio autoplay loop>
    <source src="happybirthday.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
</audio>

<div class="hearts"></div>

<div class="sparkle" style="left:10%;top:15%;">✨</div>
<div class="sparkle" style="right:15%;top:20%;">⭐</div>
<div class="sparkle" style="left:20%;bottom:20%;">💖</div>
<div class="sparkle" style="right:10%;bottom:10%;">✨</div>

<div class="container">

<h1>Happy Birthday Ja! 🎂</h1>
<div class="subtitle">Click the envelope, my lovely sister. 💌</div>

<div class="envelope" onclick="openLetter()" id="env">

<div class="back"></div>
<div class="letter">
💖 Open Me 💖
</div>
<div class="flap"></div>

</div>

</div>

<div class="popup" id="popup">

<div class="close" onclick="closeLetter()">✖</div>

<h2>To My Dearest Ja 💗</h2>

<p>

Hello, Ja! How are you? I just want to wish you a happy birthday. I know I already greeted you in our chat, but I wanted to greet you this way too.

It’s been 3 years since I met you during our campaign—3 years na rin tayong magkaibigan, mag-sisters, and bffs. At first, akala ko hindi tayo magiging close, but I’m really grateful to the student council for letting me meet a wonderful soul like you.

You’re one of the purest and most genuine friends I’ve ever had in my life. I’m just really glad and thankful for the memories, laughter, and happiness we’ve shared.

Ja, bilang kaibigan mo, alam ko kung gaano at ano ang mga pinagdaraanan mo ngayon. Hindi mo man sabihin, hindi ko man makita, pero nararamdaman ko—kilala kita eh.

I may not be by your side right now, but I want you to know that we’re here to hug and embrace you, even when it feels like the world is crashing down on you.

I’m here not only as your bff or your sister, but as someone who shares the same struggles you’re facing.

Sa haba ng taon na nakasama kita at nabati tuwing birthday mo, palagi at lagi kong hihilingin na makuha mo ang kaarawan na deserve mo.

Kasi you deserve the same joy you share with others.

I wish you a happy, happy birthday, Ja.

Sobrang miss ka na namin.

Gusto naming sumaya ka, kasi deserve at kailangan mo 'yun.

Magpagaling ka, Jaja.

Mag-iingat ka palagi.

Happy, happy birthday, my ate! 💖

</p>

<div class="footer">
Love always,<br>
Your BFF 💕
</div>

</div>

<script>

function openLetter(){
document.getElementById("env").classList.add("open");

setTimeout(()=>{
document.getElementById("popup").classList.add("show");
},900);

}

function closeLetter(){
document.getElementById("popup").classList.remove("show");
}

function createHeart(){

const heart=document.createElement("div");
heart.className="heart";
heart.innerHTML=["💖","🎂 ","💗","🎁 ","🌸","✨"][Math.floor(Math.random()*6)];
heart.style.left=Math.random()*100+"vw";
heart.style.animationDuration=6+Math.random()*6+"s";
heart.style.fontSize=(20+Math.random()*25)+"px";

document.querySelector(".hearts").appendChild(heart);

setTimeout(()=>{
heart.remove();
},12000);

}

setInterval(createHeart,500);

</script>

</body>
</html>
